788
00:43:49,467 --> 00:43:55,749
us on our quest to go and restore the light to to sort of help her survive pretty much.

789
00:43:55,749 --> 00:44:01,291
But then somewhere along the way, this starts to get vague, he got corrupted, became a monster

790
00:44:01,291 --> 00:44:07,033
pretty much, and then we have to sort of dispose of him and have a very strong emotional beat,

791
00:44:07,033 --> 00:44:07,593
pretty much.

