00:44:14,655 --> 00:44:18,896
Basically, the water in the entirety of the world of Nihlwin, the game world,

795
00:44:18,896 --> 00:44:21,337
was corrupted at the beginning of the game.

796
00:44:21,337 --> 00:44:25,139
And it actually hurts you if you're trying to swim in it.

797
00:44:25,139 --> 00:44:29,661
And so he tells us there's a reason for that.

798
00:44:29,661 --> 00:44:33,062
It's that this old water mill called the Wellspring,

799
00:44:33,062 --> 00:44:35,263
the wheels have stopped turning years and years ago.

800
00:44:35,755 --> 00:44:38,076
And if we can find a way to clear that corruption

801
00:44:38,076 --> 00:44:40,877
and start the wheels flowing, turning again,

802
00:44:40,877 --> 00:44:43,177
then the water would flow clear.

803
00:44:43,177 --> 00:44:45,098
And so that's our objective.

804
00:44:45,098 --> 00:44:47,059
And we would go to the water mill,

805
00:44:47,059 --> 00:44:48,999
we would unblock whatever is blocking it,

806
00:44:48,999 --> 00:44:50,500
the water would rush clear

807
00:44:50,500 --> 00:44:52,701
and we'd have this epic escape sequence.

808
00:44:52,701 --> 00:44:54,101
And then we would go back to cool lock

809
00:44:54,101 --> 00:44:57,983
and everything would be great pretty much.

810
00:44:57,983 --> 00:44:59,883
But then basically after that,

811
00:44:59,883 --> 00:45:02,684
we would do the whole thing in the silent woods.

812
00:45:02,684 --> 00:45:03,965
He would say, he's gonna go help us on our search.

813
00:45:04,615 --> 00:45:08,598
The idea was that at that point in this sort of darker sort of

814
00:45:08,598 --> 00:45:12,000
scene that we have of him on the left there, that was sort of the

815
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:15,002
signifier that something's not right, that he's already been

