00:45:18,484 --> 00:45:21,767
that also felt kind of weird, the fact that he asked us to

818
00:45:21,767 --> 00:45:24,949
clear the water, but actually it was too late anyway, we couldn't

819
00:45:24,949 --> 00:45:28,931
have changed the outcome, right. But in any case, then all of a

