00:46:39,817 --> 00:46:42,757
throughout the watermill that you

842
00:46:42,757 --> 00:46:45,258
have to unblock to get the wheels turning again.

843
00:46:45,258 --> 00:46:48,059
And so it all started to sort of make sense.

844
00:46:48,059 --> 00:46:50,760
And then the idea being that this foul presence eventually

845
00:46:50,760 --> 00:46:54,021
would get washed out of the watermill

846
00:46:54,021 --> 00:46:55,681
and then eventually corrupt QuoLock.

847
00:46:55,681 --> 00:46:57,001
But I'll get there.

848
00:46:58,356 --> 00:47:01,057
And so the idea being that after that escape happened,

849
00:47:01,057 --> 00:47:02,358
you have a small cut scene.

