00:47:02,358 --> 00:47:03,799
And in that cut scene in the background,

851
00:47:03,799 --> 00:47:06,520
you can see on the left that the stink spirit is kind

852
00:47:06,520 --> 00:47:07,941
of swimming under the water.

853
00:47:07,941 --> 00:47:09,482
And that's sort of for observant players

854
00:47:09,482 --> 00:47:12,643
to realize that the stink spirit isn't quite gone yet.

855
00:47:12,643 --> 00:47:13,984
It's still around.

856
00:47:13,984 --> 00:47:16,725
But that doesn't pay off until much later in the game.

