00:47:16,725 --> 00:47:21,068
But then in Act 2, when the player is exploring and then

858
00:47:21,068 --> 00:47:22,728
going through the different environments

859
00:47:22,728 --> 00:47:23,849
they can find in the game.

860
00:47:24,448 --> 00:47:30,973
they start to enter an area called the Luma Pools, and that's the area where Qolok is the boss of.

