00:47:47,587 --> 00:47:52,308
in the luma pools that we have to break and destroy and unblock things and stuff.

865
00:47:52,308 --> 00:47:55,629
And so once again an observant player might put two and two together

866
00:47:55,629 --> 00:47:59,090
and start to realize that this thing is not dead and it's gone

867
00:47:59,090 --> 00:48:03,832
this way pretty much. Then the other part of the puzzle

868
00:48:03,832 --> 00:48:10,774
is that we we add small NPC moments that basically explain that Kolok has

869
00:48:10,774 --> 00:48:13,795
actually gone to this location. So you have these

