00:49:02,817 --> 00:49:05,478
moment, where we would clear out the space that otherwise

889
00:49:05,478 --> 00:49:06,378
was filled with gameplay.

890
00:49:06,963 --> 00:49:11,206
plop this giant toad in there and actually interact with him like we did in the early

891
00:49:11,206 --> 00:49:12,127
sections of the game.

892
00:49:12,127 --> 00:49:14,308
And at the end of this interaction...

893
00:49:14,804 --> 00:49:18,526
He basically says that he will continue searching for this wisp

